---
import Base from "../layout/base.astro";
import "../style/main.css"
import Member from "../components/member.astro";
---

<Base 
title='About Us'
description="Welcome to our About Page! We specialize in web development, graphic design, and computer repairs. With a passion for technology and a commitment to excellence."
keywords="web development, graphic design, computer repairs, about page"
>
    <main class="bg-procyon-purple relative text-white md:mb-0 mb-44">
        

        <div class=" m-auto p-0 md:py-14 h-90v justify-between  w-4/5  text-white z-10  opacity-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center relative">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 -scale-x-100"  id="anchor">
                <img src="/images/astabt1.png" alt="" class="float"  id="eyes">
            </div>            
            <p class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl w-full md:w-1/3 text-center italic font-extrabold mb-10">
                Two Friends, <br>
                One Dream.
            </p>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
                <img src="/images/astabt2.webp" alt="" class="float second">
            </div>
         
        </div>
    </main>
        
    <div class="w-5/6 md:w-3/4 m-auto relative">

        <p class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl text-center font-extrabold mb-16">
			Meet The Dream Team
		</p>

        <div class="planet w-5/12 absolute -top-10 -left-1/4 z-0 blur-sm">
			<img alt="a planet" src="/images/planet7.png" alt="" class="w-full relative glow6 z-0" id="red-planet">
		</div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-20">
            <Member 
            name="Anav Chand" 
            image="/images/anav.png"
            role="Fronted Developer" 
            studies="Year 1 BSE @ USP" 
            website="Portfolio" 
            websiteUrl="https://anav.netlify.app/" 
            githubUrl=""
            igUrl=""
            gmilUrl=""
            phoneNumbr=""
            />
            <Member 
            name="Rudr Prasad" 
            image="/images/rudr.png"
            role="Software Engineer" 
            studies="Year 1 BSE @ USP" 
            website="Portfolio" 
            websiteUrl="https://anav.netlify.app/" 
            githubUrl=""
            igUrl=""
            gmilUrl=""
            phoneNumbr=""
            />
        </div>

        


        <p class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl text-center font-extrabold mb-10">
			A Little About Procyon
		</p>
        

        <p class="mb-32 text-secondary-color z-40">Procyon is a binary star system in the constallation Canis Minor. Its the one of the brightest in the night sky and has alot of signifiance in several cultures. However, to us, Procyon signifies friendship, the life-long bond of two friends. Alone, the stars of Porcyon will be invisible to the naked but but together is a spectacle to behold</p>
        

    </div>

</Base>


<style>
.glow6{
        -webkit-filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 50px rgb(240, 130, 9));
        filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 50px rgb(240, 180, 190));
    }

</style>

<script>

const redPlanet= document.getElementById("red-planet")

window.addEventListener("scroll", function(){

        let value = window.scrollY;
       
    
        redPlanet.style.top = value * 0.15 + "px"
        
       


    })
</script>

